    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use <code>stream</code> in java 8.</p>\n\n<pre><code>String[] array = list.stream().toArray(String[]::new);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Then the array can be used in the <code>...args</code> position.</p>\n"
