    "body" : "<p>in case of long (primitive value)</p>\n<pre><code>long[] longArray = list.stream().mapToLong(o-&gt;g.getValue()).toArray();\n</code></pre>\n<p>when <code>getValue()</code> returns a long type</p>\n"
